name: Desert Sorceress (Dark Souls 2 - outfit)
description:
Would appreciate images, feedback, requests, reviews, and of course comments in the comments. Please check out my other models if you like this one.

A Lora based on everyone's first playthrough outfit, the desert sorceress set.

weights 0.6 - 1 ( 1 might change artstyle or distort image)

recommended tags: thighhighs, elbow_gloves, navel, underwear,

optional tags: shaded_face, hood, fan, holding, fireball,

sadly seems like it can't do the full effect of the hood covering the face (might be a better tag). If not wanting fire or the fan I recommend putting: fan, holding, fire, fireball; in the negative prompt since it likes to gen them.
